element.name: Comments
element.value:
The Blood Wood is the resting place of the Ruins of Tal'Ra Dal, an ancient city of a long forgotten people.
Bones of the fallen and ancient war machines litter the landscape. Serving as a reminder of the great battles and wars that where fought here so long ago.
The land reeks of death and rot. One can almost feel deaths icey touch......... or is it just the bitter cold wind?
